title: Truth Phoenix (Election Edition) Pdf
description:
Truth Phoenix (Election Edition) Pdf
------------------------------------

This book is a collection of poems and reflections written over a period of 26 years (1989 - 2015) by a Vancouver writer.

These two Pdf files contain the same book.

- The Digital Edition is for those who prefer to read
on monitors, laptops, tablets, or phones.

- The Print Edition is for those who prefer to read
hard copy. It has been arranged to enable double-sided
printing into a booklet.

Peace, love, and transparency... E:)
